quote_raw: Yes, I must go to the railway station, and if he's not there, then go there and catch him. Anna looked at the railway timetable in the newspapers. An evening train went at two minutes past eight. "Yes, I shall be in time."
title: Anna Karenina
author: Leo Tolstoy
